sr - screenshot utility
=======================
sr is a quick and tiny screenshot utility for X.

Requirements
------------
sr requires Xlib and imlib2 to build.

Installation
------------
sr comes with a Makefile and config.mk file for configurable building and
testing.  Edit the latter to match your local setup (sr is installed into the
/usr/local namespace by default, you may need to modify your $PATH).

sr can be built and installed with the following command (run as root).

    make clean install

